---
layout: layout.njk
permalink: "/index.html"
title: "The Mature Feminine: A Field Guide"
---

<h1 class="mb-1">{{ siteContent.title }}</h1>
<p class="text-center fst-italic text-muted">{{ siteContent.subtitle }}</p>

<div class="text-center my-3">
  <img src="assets/images/cover.jpeg" alt="Cover image for The Mature Feminine: A Field Guide" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
</div>

{% if siteContent.quote %}
<p class="quote text-center fst-italic my-3 text-muted">“{{ siteContent.quote.text }}”<br><span class="d-block mt-1">— {{ siteContent.quote.author }}</span></p>
{% endif %}

<h2 class="mt-4">How to Use This Guide</h2>
<ul>
  {% for item in siteContent.howToUse %}
  <li><strong>{{ item.label }}:</strong> {{ item.text }}</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<h2 class="mt-4">The Four Poles of Mature Feminine</h2>
{% for pole in siteContent.poles %}
<div class="p-3 my-3 border-start border-primary-subtle bg-light-subtle">
  <h3 class="h5 mb-1">{{ pole.name }}</h3>
  <p class="mb-0">{{ pole.description }}</p>
</div>
{% endfor %}

<h2 class="mt-4">Developmental Wheel</h2>
<p>A quick map of the feminine life arc:</p>
<ul>
  {% for d in siteContent.devWheel %}
  <li><strong>{{ d.stage }}</strong> → {{ d.task }}</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<h2 class="mt-4">Quick Reference</h2>
<p>One-line essence + primary shadows for all feminine archetypes:</p>
{% for block in siteContent.quickRef %}
<h4 class="h6 mt-3">{{ block.pole }}:</h4>
<ul>
  {% for it in block.items %}
  <li><strong>{{ it.name }}</strong> – {{ it.essence }}; active: {{ it.active }}, passive: {{ it.passive }}.</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
{% endfor %}

<h2 class="mt-4">Shadow Alchemy (fast diagnostics)</h2>
<p>Quick remedies when you recognize shadow patterns:</p>
<ul>
  {% for tip in siteContent.shadowAlchemy %}
  <li>{{ tip }}</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<h2 class="mt-4">Self-assessment prompts (pick 3 today)</h2>
<ul>
  {% for q in siteContent.selfAssessment %}
  <li>{{ q }}</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>

<h2 class="mt-5">Browse Archetypes</h2>
<div class="row g-3">
  {% for group in archetypes.groups %}
  <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
    <div class="card h-100">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">{{ group.name }}</h5>
        <p class="card-text small text-muted">{{ group.summary }}</p>
        <ul class="small">
          {% for item in group.items %}
          <li><a href="{{ group.slug }}/{{ item.slug }}/">{{ item.name }}</a></li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
